}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== The unit P/N on the label of the device populating this entry. 61-20568-40. This particular unit is an '''A''' revision unit. :"T2921004P3BZ0" (and a date code of '''0016''') is silkscreened on the board.
The '''CNet''' 18-1B-UB04-FB may be identical to this device.
The power adapter included with the unit seems to be an unbranded MKD-48062100 (120VAC ~ 60Hz, 25W -> 6VDC, 2100mA, manuf. in Taiwan).
